  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Make Christmas special for DRC street children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We like Christmas to be special for all the children we support at Kimbilio. Each year we have a special party.  We make sure all the children get a present. For children who have been living on the streets an event like this is a big deal &amp; being offered a present rather than begging on the streets means a lot.  This year we opened a Primary School for over 150 former street children &amp; children whose families can&apos;t afford to send them to school. We&apos;d like them to have a party &amp; present too.</narrative>
  </description>
